name: Crest Logo T-Shirt
description:
This White American Apparel Summer T-shirt features The Discourse Clothing Crest on the front.
  • The ultralight, Sheer Jersey T-shirt is 100% Sheer Jersey cotton, combed for softness and comfort.
  • Rib cotton, stretchable collar for increased comfort and durability
  • Reinforced shoulder construction to maintain shape through repeated washings
  • Durable double-stitched bottom hem
  • Please note that our shirts fits slightly slimmer and longer than most other T-Shirts.
  • 100% made in the USA
  • Design by Trace Gough.

name: Back To The Future T-Shirt
description:
This Grey American Apparel “Track t-shirt” features an artistic design on the front
of the Delorian from Back to the Future.
Enjoy everything you love about the fit, feel, and durability of a vintage t-shirt, in a brand new version.
The print on the shirt says

	“discourse to the clothing” 
“where were going we dont need roads”

	Tri-Blend (50% Polyester / 25% Cotton / 25% Rayon) construction
